### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = TU_TOKEN_AQUI

### ==========================================
### ALBARANES
### ==========================================

### Crear albarán de materiales
POST {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "project": "ID_DEL_PROYECTO",
  "client": "ID_DEL_CLIENTE",
  "format": "material",
  "description": "Entrega de cemento para la obra",
  "workDate": "2026-04-15",
  "material": "Cemento Portland",
  "quantity": 50,
  "unit": "sacos"
}

### Crear albarán de horas simple
POST {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "project": "ID_DEL_PROYECTO",
  "client": "ID_DEL_CLIENTE",
  "format": "hours",
  "description": "Jornada de instalación eléctrica",
  "workDate": "2026-04-16",
  "hours": 8
}

### Crear albarán de horas con varios trabajadores
POST {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "project": "ID_DEL_PROYECTO",
  "client": "ID_DEL_CLIENTE",
  "format": "hours",
  "description": "Equipo de pintura en planta baja",
  "workDate": "2026-04-17",
  "workers": [
    { "name": "Juan López", "hours": 6 },
    { "name": "María García", "hours": 7 },
    { "name": "Pedro Ruiz", "hours": 5 }
  ]
}

### Listar albaranes (con paginación)
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar albaranes (filtrar por proyecto)
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote?project=ID_DEL_PROYECTO
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar albaranes (filtrar por cliente)
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote?client=ID_DEL_CLIENTE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar albaranes de tipo horas
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote?format=hours
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar albaranes firmados
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote?signed=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar albaranes por rango de fechas
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote?from=2026-01-01&to=2026-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener un albarán concreto
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote/ID_DEL_ALBARAN
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Descargar albarán en PDF
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote/pdf/ID_DEL_ALBARAN
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Firmar albarán (enviar imagen de firma como multipart)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote/ID_DEL_ALBARAN/sign
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=firma

--firma
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="signature"; filename="firma.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./firma.png
--firma--

### Eliminar albarán (solo si no está firmado)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote/ID_DEL_ALBARAN
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
